  "name": "Relentless Rage",
  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>Starting at 11th level, your rage can keep you fighting despite grievous wounds. If you drop to 0 hit points while you're raging and don't die outright, you can make a DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">10</span> Constitution saving throw. If you succeed, you drop to 1 hit point instead.</p><p>Each time you use this feature after the first, the DC increases by 5. When you finish a short or long rest, the DC resets to 10.</p></div>",
